1. Project Overview
The Bus Management App is a mobile app that digitizes daily bus operations for drivers, conductors, and management. It tracks trips, passenger count, ticket collection, and generates daily reports â€“ making bus operations efficient 

2. Project Statement
A mobile app to simplify and digitize daily bus operations, reducing paperwork and improving efficiency for transport management.

3. Objective
- Digitize trip details, passenger count, ticket collection
- Provide real-time data for management
- Improve efficiency, transparency, and reliability in bus operations

4. How it Works
1. Driver starts/ends trip via app
2. Conductor enters passenger count, ticket amount
3. Data saved, daily report generated
4. Management monitors real-time data

